room_title: Escape room "The Nautical Room" by Will You Escape the OBX in Southern Shores
review: We have never done and escape room and thought what a great experience on our annual vacation. Janet and Grace were so welcoming and I loved Janet’s passion!We signed up for the nautical room and found out quickly “this is not so easy” Janet checked on us, keeping us moving along.We had a blast and will be back! A must do!
